OL,4,G2310FElkie Brooks: In Concert 1987
OL,5,     GIn a performance recorded
OL,6,     Gespecially for the BBC at the
OL,7,     GNEC, Birmingham, Elkie produces a
OL,8,     Gsubtle blend of rock numbers and
OL,9,     Ggentle ballads.
OL,10,G2350FElkie Brooks in Concert 1987
OL,11,     GIn the second part of this
OL,12,     Gconcert, Elkie performs new
OL,13,     Gcompositions and hits such as
OL,14,     GLilac Wine, Don't Cry Out Loud
OL,15,     Gand Gasoline Alley.
